text: Raggare! (in the UK released as Blackjackets) is a 1959 Swedish adventure drama movie directed by Olle Hellbom and starring Inga Edwards, Christina Schollin, Hans Wahlgren, Bill Magnusson, Sven Holmberg. It was distributed by AB Europa Studios. ==Other websites== * Category:1959 drama movies Category:1959 adventure movies Category:Swedish drama movies Category:Swedish adventure movies
